`]}),`
`,n.jsxs(e.p,{children:[n.jsx(e.strong,{children:"Low Risk, High Reward Investments"})," are the types of investment where you are investing your time in learning and sharpening your skills in the technology that you are proficient in."]}),`
`,n.jsxs(e.p,{children:["On the other hand, ",n.jsx(e.strong,{children:"High Risk, High Reward Investments"})," are those investments in the knowledge portfolio, where you are not sure about the future of that technology but currently is in the trends."]}),`
`,n.jsx(e.p,{children:"You should aim to find emerging technologies and learn them before they become popular."}),`
`,n.jsxs(e.blockquote,{children:[`
`,n.jsx(e.h1,{children:" Learning Java when it first came out may have been risky, but it paid off handsomely for the early adopters who are now at the top of that field. "}),`
